Title: distinctDynamicTypes
Description: Calculates the list of distinct data types stored in Dynamic column.
The sorted list of data type names Array(String).
Examples: DROP TABLE IF EXISTS test_dynamic;CREATE TABLE test_dynamic(d Dynamic) ENGINE = Memory;INSERT INTO test_dynamic VALUES (42), (NULL), ('Hello'), ([1, 2, 3]), ('2020-01-01'), (map(1, 2)), (43), ([4, 5]), (NULL), ('World'), (map(3, 4))
